name: ZAMBOANGA CITY
description: I've been to Zamboanga City, Philippines countless times and I would always end up a long travel day at Paseo de Mar watching the sunset while salivating over my Knickerbocker, a localized version of a famous Filipino dessert called "halo-halo". With generous slices of mango, apple, banana, watermelon, shaved ice, sweet milk, topped by large scoops of strawberry ice cream, every spoon is truly a moment!
